Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:08.68,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs33\fax-0.03\fsp0\frz9\pos(825,525)}声带
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:08.68,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs33\fax-0.03\fsp0\frz8.5\pos(470,705)}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:08.68,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs33\fax-0.03\fsp0\frz9\pos(840,645)}不明（无异常）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:08.68,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs33\fax-0.03\fsp0\frz8.5\pos(487.5,825)}我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:08.68,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs33\fax-0.03\fsp0\frz8\pos(855,762)}左耳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个 风前辈没听说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,满开的后遗症？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈失去了味觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡左耳听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,发生满开的人无一例外？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈… 告诉我一声就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是友奈的脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了不让大家担心 所以没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真符合她的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,风前辈没听大赦说过什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,大赦的各位也都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不是风前辈的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而且身体状况肯定很快就会恢复的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 医院的大夫也这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,总之等大赦的回信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,满开的后遗症…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那算什么
Comment: 0,1:59:59.97,1:59:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我今后要怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.91,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fs45}和宿命点的战斗后，身体没有奇怪的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.17,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fs45}没有啊，出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.67,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fs45}发生满开的人，身体某处出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是指我以外的所有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么说 友奈和东乡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我… 只有我没有负伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是说我最没派上用场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明是为了战斗才来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,津国难波梦春景
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一苇枯叶渡秋风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,本以为春天来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,却只剩枯叶了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是说开心的日子总是过得那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,和东乡同学聊天时 时间总是很快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你借我做网页的书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
